## 7. What-If Scenarios (Future)

### 7.1 Scenario Mode

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  MODE: [● BASELINE]  [○ SCENARIO: "Strike Impact"]          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                              │
│  DELTA FROM BASELINE:                                        │
│  • OPEX 2026: +$2.3M (+4.2%)  ▲                             │
│  • Overrun Risk: 12 trains    ▲                             │
│  • Compliance: 94% → 89%      ▼                             │
│                                                              │
│  [Discard] [Compare Side-by-Side] [Apply to Baseline]        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 7.2 Event Sourcing

Store changes as immutable events for full audit trail:

```typescript
type ScheduleEvent =
  | { type: 'TaskScheduled'; taskId: string; startDate: Date }
  | { type: 'TaskRescheduled'; taskId: string; newStart: Date; reason: string }
  | { type: 'ConflictDetected'; taskIds: string[]; conflictType: string }
  | { type: 'ScenarioCreated'; scenarioId: string; baselineId: string };
```

